# “””
academic_plot.py  –  Library file  (do not edit for daily use)

Academic-grade Excel → Matplotlib plotter.

Default figure size  : half-A4 width  (105 mm × 80 mm)
Supported outputs    : PDF · SVG · PNG · TIFF · EPS
Dual Y-axis          : primary (left) + optional secondary (right)
Per-series control   : marker · linestyle · colour · error bars · alpha
Auto OS theme        : detects macOS / Windows / GNOME dark mode

## Dependencies

```
pip install matplotlib pandas openpyxl
```

## Public API

```
Classes   : Series · AxisConfig · LegendConfig · GridConfig · FigureConfig
Function  : plot_academic(...)  →  (fig, ax1)
Galleries : MARKER_GALLERY · LINE_GALLERY   (human-readable key → mpl code)
```

